	(197, 1, '2015-03-05 03:03:13', '2015-03-05 03:03:13', '<body id="other" class="page page-id-13 page-parent page-template page-template-page-about-php win8.1 chrome chrome-0">\r\n<section class="intro-image" style="background-image: url(&#39;<?php echo get_template_directory_uri(); ?>/images/cki-template11-headers-about.jpg&#39;);">\r\n                <header>\r\n                    <h1>About the Quality of Life Measures</h1>\r\n                    <hr>\r\n                </header>\r\n            </section>\r\n            <div class="row">\r\n                <section class="post standard">\r\n                    <div class="row clearfix">\r\n                        <header class="large-3 medium-3 small-12 columns">\r\n                            <h2>About the Project</h2>\r\n                            <hr>\r\n                        </header>\r\n                        <article class="large-8 large-offset-1 medium-8 medium-offset-1 small-12 columns">\r\n                            <p>What is wellbeing?</p>\r\n                            <p>Throughout human history, philosophers, poets, theologians, and scholars have sought the answer to that seemingly simple question. From Kong Solomon to the city squares of ancient Greece to the worldwide conversations of the Internet age, humanity has discussed and debated just what the good life means—and how to help more people achieve it.</p>\r\n                            <a class="btn flat gray " href="<?php echo home_url(); ?>/about-the-project/#about_the_project">Learn More</a>\r\n                        </article>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                </section>\r\n                <section class="post standard">\r\n                    <div class="row clearfix">\r\n                        <header class="large-3 medium-3 small-12 columns">\r\n                            <h2>Advisory Board</h2>\r\n                            <hr>\r\n                        </header>\r\n                        <article class="large-8 large-offset-1 medium-8 medium-offset-1 small-12 columns">\r\n                            <p>The Baugh Center’s Advisory Board is comprised of a diverse group of regular people, scholars, business owners, and thought leaders who bring a variety of perspectives to the table. Their feedback are critical to fostering an informed and thoughtful dialogue on quality of life. Advisory Board members provide strategic guidance for continuous improvement in the quality and value of our project.</p>\r\n                            <a class="btn flat gray " href="<?php echo home_url(); ?>/advisory-board">Learn More</a>\r\n                        </article>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                </section>\r\n                <section class="post standard">\r\n                    <div class="row clearfix">\r\n                        <header class="large-3 medium-3 small-12 columns">\r\n                            <h2>Our Contributors</h2>\r\n                            <hr>\r\n                            </header>\r\n                            <article class="large-8 large-offset-1 medium-8 medium-offset-1 small-12 columns">\r\n                            <p>The Quality of Life Measures Advisory Board is comprised of a diverse group of esteemed scholars, business leaders, and thought leaders who bring a variety of perspectives to the project. These experts and their feedback are critical to efforts to foster an informed and thoughtful dialogue on project. Advisory Board members provide strategic guidance for continuous improvement in the quality and value of the project’s research.</p>\r\n                            <a class="btn flat gray jump" href="<?php echo home_url(); ?>/research">Meet our Contributors</a>\r\n                        </article>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                </section>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <script type="text/javascript">\r\n            	jQuery.noConflict();\r\n                	(function( $ ) {$(function() {$("#